Question(questionText, choices, correctAnswer)

Question holds question info and user's answer without. They are privately
owned by quiz objects so they won't be visible to the user objects. Because
of this, information hiding will be nearly non-existent.

*****************
public
*****************

.questionText                   string

.choices                        array of strings

.correctAnswer                  int

.userAnswer                     int
    Starts at Undefined

*****************
privileged
*****************

.isCorrect()                    r bool
    Checks if userAnswer is the same as correctAnswer